Package view

Class GameCallbackGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • view.GameCallbackGroup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GameCallback, GameCallbackCollection
    public class GameCallbackGroup
extends java.lang.Object
implements GameCallbackCollection, GameCallback
    Helper class to reduce code in GameEngineImpl.

    Implements both the GameCallbackCollection interface (to un/register callbacks) and the GameCallback interface (to provide the callback methods).

    Author:
    Ross Nye
